summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 24993 entitled: "An ordinance submitting to the qualified voters of the City of Seattle, at the general election to be held in such city on Tuesday, November 8, 1910, the proposition of the issuance and sale by said city, of its negotiable bonds in the sum of $1,000,000.00 for the purpose of providing money, for the construction of a City Hall Building."
